      "author": "kenanlian",
      "description": "## Card Workspace v0.1.2\n\nThis release ships the indexed-only search architecture and release/documentation updates for the Obsidian Card Workspace plugin.\n\n### Highlights\n- Replaces the fallback/no-index search path with the indexed-only search pipeline.\n- Improves scoped search empty-state behavior and copy.\n- Updates release/version metadata across package.json, manifest.json, versions.json, and package-lock.json.\n- Updates README and project documentation for release commands, validation, indexed-only search architecture, and v0.1.2 release status.\n- Includes Sisyphus/Atlas plan, evidence, and decision documentation for the indexed-search-only work.\n- Fixes the release-check issue where FolderCardPanel.svelte was missing EMPTY_PANEL_STATE.emptyStateMessage.\n\n### Validation\n- npm run release:check -- 0.1.2 passed.\n- npm run check:svelte passed with 0 errors; known Toolbar.svelte a11y warnings remain.\n- npm run check passed.\n- npm run build passed; known Toolbar.svelte a11y warnings remain.\n- npm test passed: 22 files / 402 tests.\n\n### Assets\nInstall/update manually by downloading:\n- main.js\n- manifest.json\n- styles.css\n",
